  {
    "uuid": "1a578777-cbe5-59d1-a4dc-d143d449f59c",
    "entry": "寒暁",
    "reading": {
      "primary": "かんぎょう",
      "alternatives": [
        "かんきょう"
      ],
      "is_heteronym": false
    },
    "grammar": {
      "pos": [
        "名詞"
      ],
      "ctype": null,
      "inflections": null
    },
    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "cold winter dawn",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "「うわ、冷えるな……」寒暁の空気は鋭く、吐き出す息が真っ白に固まって消えた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "寒暁の静寂を切り裂くように、除雪車の重低音が遠くの道から響き始めた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "凍てつく寒暁の中、朝市に並べる野菜を積み込む農家たちの手が忙しく動く。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "まだ星の光が鋭い寒暁の空が、東の地平線からゆっくりと藍色に解けていく。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      }
    ],
